{"tid":2248890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初衷？原來好多人已經忘記咗了","createTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-20T03:53:52.000Z","uid":43785,"like":113,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"e39d1af96382597444499992d877616cced4a726","tid":2248890,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:14.000Z","msg":"初衷？原來好多人已經忘記咗了<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iCAWvqb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiCAWvqb.jpg&h=03708f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n細細店舖，有人在排隊畀錢，有人揀麵包做早餐，有人挑選西餅，有人買生日蛋糕。簡單說，舖頭每個角落都充斥著送錢給美心的人。<br />\n<br />\n等人順道觀察一段時間，有三十出頭大好青年，手持美心西餅，毫不猶豫步出店外，浩浩蕩蕩，不知羞恥。<br />\n<br />\n轉頭又有20來歲少女同男友，走到蛋糕櫥窗前，向芒果蛋糕露出流晒口水的表情... <br />\n<br />\n正正因為，街上有不知羞恥的青年，不分黑白的少女，無知貪平貪方便的師奶，以及食黑心蛋糕大的廢老。<br />\n<br />\n這店，仍然屹立不倒。<br />\n<br />\n高風險活動，你不能參與，我理解，我明白。但連管理自己銀包的錢，不落入黑心企業，有咁難咩？<br />\n<br />\n成班後生情侶排隊食元氣，送錢畀一間狂言要放棄年青人的舖頭？我覺得好醜。<br />\n<br />\n連叫一間黑心企業執笠，也做不到。遑論爭取難度過百倍的事？<br />\n<br />\n有些習慣，要戒。<br />\n有些店舖，要罷。<br />\n有些壽司，要轉。<br />\n<br />\n講到臭，善用手上每一蚊，是最基本的義務。"},{"pid":"b3925c3e9685d342019127236bc35eca7ea748ec","tid":2248890,"uid":27601,"like":8,"dislike":6,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:32.000Z","msg":"你點記得的"},{"pid":"e3b63f4502b41a167c017550e3606b2d612c44c8","tid":2248890,"uid":199227,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:32.000Z","msg":"yes sir"},{"pid":"15361dc760d5ef80a848fbdb279bc518fbb25ba0","tid":2248890,"uid":143499,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:07:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"639e28a036c94596e58c96dbde3bc1e4dcdad002","tid":2248890,"uid":143499,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:08:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4f2d4c46ef0c61b351f9b56915226df2b940e6c3","tid":2248890,"uid":8014,"like":11,"dislike":8,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:09:27.000Z","msg":"最多下個月雙11 淘寶買少啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nsorry sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4aeb70254c7612ad01de6f89104213164b1d796","tid":2248890,"uid":210807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5eb610c7ebea87deeb6ac080b8a2c8163767f9","tid":2248890,"uid":65888,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:10:13.000Z","msg":"鳩蛇開認真po推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"255f134e13fc6c8c682aa6f8d69e9f4cdc90260b","tid":2248890,"uid":119639,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:16:45.000Z","msg":"你忘記左venus未先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbc1b5f7c7e36dc8e83df3ab15973ed5a207d9d8","tid":2248890,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:18:11.000Z","msg":"Yes sir!Good morning sir!"},{"pid":"e9c84de6e7de2b1bcaa88968969188a28521e83f","tid":2248890,"uid":43785,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:24:09.000Z","msg":"推啦，屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eef401aaf5df4649242a1ea3da5f7267eb158ba","tid":2248890,"uid":366470,"like":7,"dislike":4,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"係咪得我一個仲堅持緊拒絕紅店藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"028400d7992c3d8a4690ce1f1ab722459d217232","tid":2248890,"uid":60000,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no